10:21.054 --> 10:23.857 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And there aren't that many
people who are
willing to change their minds.

10:23.890 --> 10:27.093 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, just because
I know it's
complicated, Mary Agnes, but why
has this

10:27.126 --> 10:28.461 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
happened?

10:28.495 --> 10:30.463 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARY AGNES CAREY: Well, it's
