their products to try to get
more market share.

10:33.633 --> 10:36.603 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And now they are going to have
to even that
out.

10:36.636 --> 10:40.139 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We may have had -- likely have
had a lot of
sicker people get in first.

10:40.173 --> 10:42.208 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Everyone sort of knew that when
they did the
Affordable Care Act.

10:42.242 --> 10:43.676 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
The sickest people come first.

10:43.710 --> 10:46.045 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
