11:19.946 --> 11:21.814 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BETH PLEIN, Maryland: My name is
Beth Plein.

11:21.848 --> 11:23.483 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
