12:53.272 --> 12:55.041 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, of course, we have this
requirement for
coverage.

12:55.074 --> 13:01.180 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, Reid, we
just heard her
say, she said, I wish -- she
