36:31.122 --> 36:36.461 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: When did
it become
the kind of word that is so
controversial

36:36.494 --> 36:38.263 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
