who have the idea of taking
nigger back.

38:28.406 --> 38:33.111 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, you have some people who
say, well, nigger
has been used to take us down.

38:33.144 --> 38:39.150 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What we are going to do is grab
this word
