our own purposes.

38:39.184 --> 38:41.286 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: But do
they know the
history of it?

38:41.319 --> 38:45.256 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
RANDALL KENNEDY: Well, one of
the reasons
I wrote a book about this was
because I got

38:45.290 --> 38:54.032 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the sense that there were
especially young
people who were using the word
who didn't

38:54.065 --> 38:58.469 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
have an understanding of the
history behind
the word.

38:58.503 --> 39:04.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, I spent 40 pages just giving
instance
after instance after instance of
the way in

39:05.009 --> 39:08.279 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
which this word has been used to
hurt black
people.

39:08.313 --> 39:14.319 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Hasn't
it also been
used against other ethnic
groups, Chinese,

39:14.352 --> 39:15.753 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
