39:15.787 --> 39:21.659 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RANDALL KENNEDY: It's the atomic
bomb of racial
slurs.

39:21.693 --> 39:32.637 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It is the racial slur that has
been used in
other contexts, so, for
instance, Palestinians,

39:32.670 --> 39:38.509 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the niggers of the Middle East,
the Irish,
the niggers of Europe.

39:38.543 --> 39:42.747 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
This is a term that has been
generalized around
the world.

39:42.780 --> 39:48.453 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you want to put somebody
down, analogize
them to the nigger.

39:48.486 --> 39:52.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Given
the power of
this particular word that we are
discussing,

39:52.523 --> 39:56.094 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the power of it to wound, what
is the solution
to that?

39:56.127 --> 39:59.097 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
RANDALL KENNEDY: I don't think
there is a
solution, other than education.

39:59.130 --> 40:05.937 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
People ought to know that even
if you are
using the word without
malevolence, even if

40:05.970 --> 40:11.943 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
