that you use
this term very carefully, if
ever.

41:15.306 --> 41:21.079 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Some of
these younger
people using it are not using
the full word.

41:21.112 --> 41:23.314 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
