tell you something.

42:28.346 --> 42:35.286 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When I hear the word nigger, I
remember when
that word was used by people who
wouldn't

42:35.319 --> 42:40.091 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
