about.

42:45.663 --> 42:46.631 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That was very powerful.

42:46.664 --> 42:47.632 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT:
Absolutely.

42:47.665 --> 42:51.436 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
RANDALL KENNEDY: That was very
powerful.

42:51.469 --> 42:55.173 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And what I said to him was: Sir,
