the infamous

43:21.699 --> 43:23.568 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
N-word.

43:23.601 --> 43:25.736 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLAYNE HUNTER-GAULT: Well,
