44:50.988 --> 44:55.593 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BILL STOWE, CEO, Des Moines
Water Works: We
have eight units here
constructed in about

44:55.626 --> 44:58.296 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
