officer of the Des Moines Water
Works.

45:02.199 --> 45:09.373 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BILL STOWE: The big challenge
cleaning up
the water in the Raccoon and Des
Moines Rivers,

45:09.407 --> 45:14.912 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
